    "description": "Are you a skilled Medical Officer looking for your next big career move? Deenanath Mangeshkar Hospital South Asia Partners in Tiruchirappalli offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Deenanath Mangeshkar Hospital South Asia Partners:\nDeenanath Mangeshkar Hospital South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Deenanath Mangeshkar Hospital South Asia Partners!",
